latestPosts.caption: Day 2 of 3 @metallica takes over PHILLY … Cause music saves us all… there are just some moments in life that just give you all the feelz. I have been in love with @kirkhammett since I was 17 years old. Seeing him nerd out about his incredible guitar collection when moments later @robtrujillo comes out to jam. What a fucking gift.  @squindo @orion_metallicatributeband @oym_metallicatribute #m72philly #metallica #metalhead #musicisagift #bangyourhead #philly #metallicatakeover #kirkhammett #robtrujillo #metallica #tonysquindo

Philadelphia. Day 1 of 3.  Pop up shops. Merch. M72. Old friends. New friends. Rain. Wind. Sun. Soft pretzels. Head Banging. Trail mix. @iceninekills @limpbizkit and most importantly @metallica 

I have been a metal head since I was 16 years old. When I heard @metallica for the first time #andjusticeforall had just released and seeing the band in 1988 was the coolest moment of my life. Like any relationship my love for them ebbed and flowed over the years so there were many tours that I missed. I guess as we all face new chapters in life seeking out things that once gave you comfort isn’t foreign. I was lucky to go to @metlifestadium in 2023 to see them waaaay up in section nose bleed. So this experience was something a little different and I am so grateful for it. @matthaas73 so good to see you! 🤘🏼🤘🏼🤘🏼🤘🏼🤘🏼🤘🏼🤘🏼☠️☠️☠️🖤🖤🖤🖤

Always on the journey for the perfect blow out…. And these two products from @azhaircare have me elevating my look.  First  I applied the Elixir Nourishing Oil to smooth my ends and give shine and bounce to my hair (BONUS this can also be used on dry hair too). And the SMELL. Ohhh lalala so deeelish.  Then after a feathery blow out with my @dysonbeauty hair dryer I applied the Smooth Serum to tame my frizzes and add some hold to my locks and more importantly some anti humectants to my very curly natural hair. 

I am excited to try these in the opposite application as well since both are versatile enough to use wet or dry. #azhaircare #azcraftluxuryhaircare #elevatedhair #elevate #haircare #thankyou #curlyhair #blowout #dyson #purplehair
